    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Magical Marketplace pg. 25</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> moderate transmutation <strong>CL</strong> 7th</p><p><strong>Slot</strong> none; <strong>Price</strong> +2 bonus; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>This special ability can only be placed on ranged weapons. Whenever the wielder attempts to make a sneak attack with a <em>sniping </em>weapon, the maximum distance she can be from her target increases to 45 feet. This ability does not stack with other abilities that increase the distance at which a ranged sneak attack may be made.</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>longshot</em><sup>UC</sup>; <strong>Price</strong> -</p>",
